    <h2 id="i">Interactive element</h2>
    <section>
        Chess has a substantial online presence with interactive platforms like Chess.com and Lichess, where players can compete against others worldwide, solve puzzles, and watch instructional videos. These platforms often feature analysis tools that help players understand their games and improve.
    </section>
